{"lastModified":1773759917731,"uri":"c::26934280528::vessel::764623f0-017e-11ef-af1a-49a51012e18e","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Base / Home Port: Olbia, Italy\nOperating Area: Italy (Sardinia, Amalfi), France (French Riviera)\n\nStep aboard the AEGEAN Explorer M26, a 26-metre marvel blending elegance, nautical ingenuity, and sustainability for 12 guests. Harmony defines its three master suites, including an upper deck master stateroom with a private terrace. Customise your journey with a preference list for entertainment and culinary delights. Enjoy spacious common areas, a swim platform, and water toys. A dedicated crew of four ensures an exceptional experience. Embrace solar-powered elegance with a range exceeding 3,500 nautical miles, ideal for extended stays and remote explorations.\n\n\n\nUKIEL Key Features:\n\nBuilt by Aegean Yacht in 2022\nThree full-beam master suites on each deck, including an upper deck master stateroom\nSteel hull with aluminium superstructure\nSolar-powered elegance, fuel efficiency, and low environmental impact\n\nExceptional gross tonnage of 187 and 3500n/M range for it's length of 26m\n\nEquipped with infotainment system YachtEye\n\nAccommodates up to 12 guests over 6 guest cabins - unique for it's length\n\nSuperb fusion of sundeck, shading, and water recreational amenities","blueprint":{"name":"UKIEL","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::764623f0-017e-11ef-af1a-49a51012e18e::assets::da16c580-be19-11ef-ac15-61911423263c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::764623f0-017e-11ef-af1a-49a51012e18e::assets::da162940-be19-11ef-ac14-61911423263c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::764623f0-017e-11ef-af1a-49a51012e18e::assets::d9eea410-be19-11ef-8112-4b5174e559f4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::764623f0-017e-11ef-af1a-49a51012e18e::assets::da15db20-be19-11ef-ac15-61911423263c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::764623f0-017e-11ef-af1a-49a51012e18e::assets::da15b410-be19-11ef